pay a heavy price.

01:07:33.949 --> 01:07:36.385
<i>And all come back
to the fold.</i>

01:07:37.751 --> 01:07:39.853
What is it?

01:07:39.855 --> 01:07:42.155
Please tell me.

01:07:42.157 --> 01:07:45.657
