from my wife.

01:10:10.771 --> 01:10:14.040
- I can't, I can't do this.
- It's okay. It's okay.

01:10:14.042 --> 01:10:15.607
- It's okay.
- Get out of my fuck...

01:10:15.609 --> 01:10:16.578
